196
00:29:24.758 --> 00:29:27.008
Ta med Bella ut!

197
00:29:27.967 --> 00:29:29.383
Bella...

198
00:29:31.008 --> 00:29:32.008
Jag...

199
00:29:34.758 --> 00:29:35.967
